  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ConfigureMenuItem
    Configure the labyrinth size.
    DocumentMenuItem

    FileMenu
    The File menu inside the menu bar.
    HelpMenu
    The Help menu inside the menu bar.
    InitMenuItem
    Initialize the labyrinth randomly.
    InstructionMenuItem
    Give help dialogue about how to play this game.
    NewMenuItem

    OpenMenuItem

    Quit this game.
